            <title>[CAMEL-17651] RouteWatcherReloadStrategy crashes on Windows or if pattern is not specified</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-17651</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On Windows, the FileFilter fails because we try to split the path using &apos;/&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If I don&apos;t set a pattern, it&apos;s set to null, and pattern.split(&apos;,&apos;) fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The doc states that the default pattern is &amp;#42;.yaml,*.xml, so it should be possible not to set a pattern.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
